snippet.title: Fortnite Chapter 3 Season 3 Cinematic Trailer
snippet.description:
Watch the Fortnite Chapter 3 Season 3 Cinematic Trailer. For more details visit: https://www.epicgames.com/fortnite/en-US/chapter-3-season-3

In Chapter 3 Season 3: Vibin’, the Island is one giant party. Bounce around in Reality Falls, ride atop creatures, brave the Screwballer coaster, and revel with new arsenal. 

Drop into Season 3 and spread the good vibes! Bring good and evil together with this Season’s Battle Pass. In addition to Darth Vader himself, the Chapter 3 Season 3 Battle Pass includes the anti-hero Evie, the defender Adira, and five more Outfits. Speaking of assembling Outfits, customize the parts of “Snap”! Later on in the Season? Unlock world famous archaeologist Indiana Jones. Play Your Way!

Sprint, climb, and smash your way to a Victory Royale whether you choose to build up in Fortnite Battle Royale or go no-builds in the new Fortnite Zero Build.
#Fortnite #FortniteChapter3Season3 #FortniteCinematicTrailer
